data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful Forest Gale Heights neighborhood! This charming property offers not only a warm and inviting atmosphere but also stunning valley views that will take your breath away. This spacious home boasts large square footage, featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, providing ample space for you and your guests. Inside, you'll find an updated kitchen. The living room has newer carpet, family has laminate flooring and both offer fireplaces, adding to the cozy and comfortable ambiance of the home. Two sliders lead to a big deck that overlooks the beautiful backyard, making it the perfect spot for enjoying the serene surroundings.  The outdoor area is a true oasis, complete with a garden shed, covered patio, and covered deck areas, creating spaces that are ideal for entertaining or simply relaxing in the fresh air. The raised garden beds are perfect for the green-thumbed enthusiast, and the mature landscaping adds to the beauty and tranquility of the yard. This is an exceptional opportunity to own a piece in Forest Gale Heights to enjoy the serene lifestyle and valley views that come with it. Don't miss your chance to make this lovely property your own. Contact an agent today to schedule a private viewing and experience the magic of this home for yourself.
